Stanhope Capital Buys Jewson Associates, Telegraph Reports

-- B y   K e i t h   J e n k i n s
-- 
2011-06-12T10:11:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-12/stanhope-capital-buys-jewson-associates-telegraph-reports.html
Stanhope Capital LLP, a wealth
management group, bought rival Jewson Associates, raising the
assets under its control to 7.5 billion pound ($12.2 billion),
the Sunday Telegraph said, citing Stanhope founder Daniel Pinto.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Keith Jenkins in  London  at 
 kjenkins3@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dick Schumacher at 
 dschumacher@bloomberg.net . 